ctedWar": [0.11, 0.06, 0.02, -0.04, -0.1, -0.16, -0.23, -0.31], "fairAav": 886883, "totalValue": 7095061}], "note": "Fair AAV = average projected annual market value over the term (aging-curve WAR walk x $4.71M/WAR, each year floored at the league minimum). Longer terms average in decline years, so the fair AAV falls. Real deals carry a term/security premium this does not model -- it is the production-fair anchor, not a prediction of the signing."}, "contractProjection": null, "contractAudit": null, "explain": {"scorecard": {"value": {"receipts": [{"label": "Even strength (5v5)", "value": "+0.66 WAR", "tone": "pos"}, {"label": "Special teams (PP + PK)", "value": "+0.24 WAR", "tone": "pos"}, {"label": "Penalty discipline (vs position)", "value": "-0.06 WAR", "tone": "neg"}, {"label": "Faceoffs", "value": "+0.00 WAR", "tone": "neutral"}, {"label": "Total, last 3 seasons", "value": "+0.41 WAR", "tone": "pos", "strong": true}], "summary": "His total on-ice value, converted to WINS (WAR). It adds up everything he does \u2014 even-strength play, the power play and penalty kill, his penalty discipline RELATIVE TO HIS POSITION (defensemen structurally take more than they draw, so only the differential vs other D counts), and faceoffs \u2014 and the grade ranks that total against other players at his position over the last three seasons.", "method": "Total WAR sums these four, each priced in wins. The grade is this player's percentile vs same-position peers over the 3-season window."}, "overall": {"receipts": [{"label": "5v5 xG impact (RAPM)", "value": "-0.05 xG/60", "tone": "neg", "strong": true}, {"label": "\u2014 offense", "value": "-0.19 xG/60", "tone": "neg"}, {"label": "\u2014 defense", "value": "+0.14 xG/60", "tone": "pos"}, {"label": "5v5 sample", "value": "3,146 min", "tone": "neutral"}, {"label": "On-ice xG share", "value": "50.4%", "tone": "neutral"}, {"label": "Relative to team (on \u2212 off ice)", "value": "+0.5%", "tone": "pos"}], "summary": "His two-way impac